Package: RNRCS
Type: Package
Title: Download and Work with NRCS data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Robert Lee <rhlee@colorado.edu>, Josh Roberti <jaroberti87@gmail.com>,
Maintainer: Robert Lee <rhlee@colorado.edu>
Description: RNRCS downloads NRCS data and metadata, currently for sites in the SCAN, SNOTEL, and SNOLITE networks. Future updates will incorporate BOR, SNOW, and USGS sites in the NRCS/AWDB network.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.1)
Imports:
    magrittr,
    rvest,
    xml2
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
